{"tid":954544,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"各位用戶請入一入來！！","createTime":"2018-12-24T16:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T17:11:13.000Z","uid":142872,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35ebe2dfa5b94a64aa3cc533b7104126a0fa267f","tid":954544,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"大家好! <br />\n<br />\n     我是曉旭的媽媽。佢出左去，但係唔記得帶手機。我看到他連登有唔少讚好，想問問大家，可以幫伯母一個忙嗎 ? <br />\n<br />\n     這個孩子從小就很獨立，不愛說話，雖然表面好像很多朋友，很堅強，很敢在連登上發文，找人做朋友，但他內心是很孤獨的...希望你們大家有空可多找他聊天。<br />\n<br />\n     聖誕節就快到了，如果可以，請大家送禮物給他，如果想不到送什麼給佢，送現金亦可。他還預備了笑容和雙手等著你們， 一齊用愛與包容幫他走出封閉的心， 你們可以幫伯母這個忙嗎？ 感謝大家...<br />\n<br />\n在此預祝各位聖誕快樂！！"},{"pid":"ee9930c27cba42b1381e8a3deb7b8423caefac6e","tid":954544,"uid":117967,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑呀屌你老味"},{"pid":"b6bbc9f65a48c06f6bf913e58059c24edaeaa76d","tid":954544,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9930c27cba42b1381e8a3deb7b8423caefac6e","tid":954544,"uid":117967,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑呀屌你老味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"幫幫忙吧好人！"},{"pid":"6001e062741d43c879b13f220967b72409392a16","tid":954544,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"果然錢係最實際。"},{"pid":"1ac366ef929ed7df876ea0e27055e0b17d2725e1","tid":954544,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"fac40b0fb0cc186f759997104f66916df7e48104","tid":954544,"uid":93761,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"793de212664e39dea9c2deb22f41022c644b4687","tid":954544,"uid":142872,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1ac366ef929ed7df876ea0e27055e0b17d2725e1","tid":954544,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16: